title: Evet project
author: Evet project
content: Join our testnet phase and get your multipliers! 63/100 users already applied.In the next few days, we will officially announce the start dates of the launch event. During the event, the top 3 users with the highest score will receive a completely FREE PoS blockchain as a prize. You can check the event's operation and how to earn points by accessing the launch event channel on discord https://discord.gg/HFSpKnAW9tFor more information on the project, you can visit our website https://evet.ink/ or read our whitepaper where everything is explained in great detail.If you have any questions about the event or the project, do not hesitate to ask us. We will be providing more information throughout the week.Follow us on Twitter https://twitter.com/EvetBlock This is going to be something big!
